name: hebrew
description: This file contains lexemes/glosses from my personal collection mixed with ETCBC lexeme and glosses.When I merged the two, I linked my personal lexemes to the ETCBC lexemes, but I kept my glosses.Any new words utilize the ETCBC gloss. All lexemes use the ETCBC surface form provided by the Text-Fabric function F.voc_utf8.v(). The lexeme node numbers are taken from version c of the ETCBC BHSA dataset.
